reviewText: Cover in excellent shape, no scratches and played awesome! What I have to write an essay to git rid of this

so you thought demons of dirt 3 was good? you aint seen nothing yet, demons of dirt 4 kicks but. Watch Carey Hart do some of his crazy death defying stunts and walk away. Awesome sound track, with loads of other cool riders. This one is a definate for any dirt biker, watch and learn boys....
